Basic Requirements: https://osp.od.nih.gov/wp-content/uploads/Non-NIH-Funded_Basic_Study_Information.pdf
Submission Portal: https://submit.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/dbgap/ 
Tamplate files: https://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/dbgap/dbGaP_Submission_Guide_Templates/Individual_Submission_Templates/ 
